    <item>
      <title>野村证券警告称，中国股市繁荣可能像 2015 年一样走向衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/china-s-stocks-boom-may-turn-to-bust-as-in-2015-nomura-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司表示，投资者应为中国股市 16 年来最大涨势的衰退做好准备，因为当前的经济基础比疫情之前要弱得多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/china-s-stocks-boom-may-turn-to-bust-as-in-2015-nomura-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 20:08:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>港口罢工最新消息：维​​尔萨克称谈判将使香蕉运上岸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/port-strike-latest-costco-shoppers-load-up-on-toilet-paper</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于码头工人与雇用他们的码头运营商及航运公司之间的劳动合同于周二到期，从休斯顿到迈阿密再到波士顿的美国集装箱港口连续第三天关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/port-strike-latest-costco-shoppers-load-up-on-toilet-paper</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 19:58:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元上涨表明交易员对全球降息路径感到担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/dollar-rally-signals-trader-angst-about-global-rate-cut-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员开始质疑美联储的降息路径与全球其他央行相比有多激进，本周美元出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/dollar-rally-signals-trader-angst-about-global-rate-cut-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 14:35:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东冲突和美国数据导致新兴货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/pause-in-china-rally-sparks-wider-drop-in-emerging-market-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东冲突推动对避险美元的需求，而美国数据支持了人们对美联储将减缓降息步伐的押注，新兴市场货币周四下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/pause-in-china-rally-sparks-wider-drop-in-emerging-market-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:49:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行计划加快降息步伐，英镑兑欧元创 2022 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/pound-hits-two-week-low-as-bailey-opens-door-to-more-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利暗示英国央行可能采取更积极的方式降低利率后，英镑兑欧元出现 2022 年底以来的最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/pound-hits-two-week-low-as-bailey-opens-door-to-more-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 05:57:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
